{
  "stem": "13471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, what do Quaker pacifists have to do with seagoing robbers, you see, under a son of a bitch like-- [LAUGHTER] --like William of Normandy, I don't believe it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, then I got to looking into it, and I looked it up in the British-- Burke's it's called.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The same Burke that-- that wrote the Same Burke.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Steer is in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there's a coat of arms, and a motto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there's a-- and two crossed oars on top.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oars.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Steersman, see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Steer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden, you know, I'm being a little more impressed by the old man's talk, see?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I thought, well, if I've got to go in one, I said, let's go back to the family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'll go in the Navy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when did you officially become a commissioned officer of the US Navy?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "20 June, 1941.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ensign, in all his glory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The lowest-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, single.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't get married till after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a Quaker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I joined the Navy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was, as I [? say ?] hell to pay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I was not a biddable son, friend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had voted for Roosevelt, that terrible sin to begin with, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I had-- I had-- Well, the point is this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said-- I told-- we had big shouting arguments, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said to my father, I said, you have sent me to the best schools.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I am-- I didn't say you, I said thee.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I used the Quaker thee and thou, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they have taught me that I have a good head, and I'm to use it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "OK, my good head says that there's a war coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my good head said it's a worthwhile thing to fight for.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
